description: The Solactive ISS ESG Developed Markets Eurozone Net Zero Pathway Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-capitalisation companies from Eurozone countries which are selected and weighted with the aim of seeking alignment with EU Paris Aligned Benchmark standards and certain net zero frameworks ESG exclusions Reviewed on a semi-annual basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.solactive.com .
name: Xtrackers EMU Net Zero Pathway Paris Aligned UCITS ETF 1C
